{"tid":2489124,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"回應飛馬電腦","createTime":"2021-04-14T17:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T17:59:51.000Z","uid":150084,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"189fb0628a7c4f50922adbb7675aaf35a70a05f1","tid":2489124,"uid":150084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"追post：<br />\n突發! 飛馬電腦PEGASUS口講顯示卡冇貨 然後轉頭大量比礦佬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2483361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2483361</a><br />\n<br />\n垃撚圾 飛馬電腦 有卡唔派貨 做臭自己個朵<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gQhBAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gQhBAS</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩飛馬電腦 林仔入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gQCAPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gQCAPS</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/314622325626313/posts/1198616507226886/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F314622325626313%2Fposts%2F1198616507226886%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=fa7e1b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/314622325626313/posts/1198616507226886/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n有鑒於網上相關投訴飛馬電腦預訂顯示卡之言論<br />\n<br />\n飛馬電腦先於此向受影響之客戶及相關人士表達歉意。亦於此澄清及回應相關言論。<br />\n<br />\n首先，飛馬電腦從三月底起已有經不同渠道 (飛馬官方網站，<a href=\"http://Price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPrice.com.hk&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=fd6f09ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Price.com.hk</a>，DCFever 等) 銷售*並無*客戶預訂之顯示卡，而單獨出售的並不包括仍有客戶預訂顯示卡型號，包括該張3080<br />\n而飛馬官網直至目前仍有 [可單買] 之顯示卡產品。<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於有顧客於 LIHKG 討論區用戶 讓治#150084 投訴於飛馬電腦預訂 RTX 3080 顯示卡<br />\n但飛馬未按下單時條款安排出貨<br />\n經過詳細審視對話及訂單紀錄後決定作出以下補償，以表歉意。<br />\n<br />\n1) 於處理訂卡訂單時後加砌機限定規則導致沒有發貨予相關顧客，我們會作出相對於該顧客下單時的訂金的兩倍，即現金賠償額外 $1000，並表示最高歉意。<br />\n2) 下星期一起, 每天中午 12:00 放出一件 $1 特惠產品回饋客戶, 限時一周, 詳情明天於 <a href=\"https://shop.pegasus.hk/2021-apr-sorry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.pegasus.hk%2F2021-apr-sorry&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=366b79c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shop.pegasus.hk/2021-apr-sorry</a> 公佈<br />\n<br />\n對於合理定價的標準，本公司是以市面可單購之產品價格進行比較，根據市場需求及供應定下俱競爭力的價錢。<br />\n<br />\n而有關 HKEPC 用戶 ventra 的投訴顯示卡價格升幅問題，<br />\n經翻查相關紀錄，我們於 2020 年 12 月 25 日起 (即 ventra 下單前)，已於官網首頁及砌機報價頁面中明確標示顯示卡狀態為 &quot;紅色&quot;。<br />\n而且於 <a href=\"https://shop.pegasus.hk/help/stockStatus#nvidia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.pegasus.hk%2Fhelp%2FstockStatus%23nvidia&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=c19f9190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shop.pegasus.hk/help/stockStatus#nvidia</a> 明確說明 (以下為 12 月 25 日原文): <br />\n「Last Update: 25-Dec 7pm 顯示卡來貨價不斷上漲, 有機會預訂價格與最終價格不一致 現貨不受影響, 訂貨若因來貨價上漲導致最終價格提升，可選擇退款，退款不設手續費」<br />\n<br />\n我們對於 ventra 的投訴感到遺憾，但本公司已清楚向顧客說明訂購熱門產品的風險，希望各位明白。<br />\n我們會於明天再次聯絡客戶安排退款或選購其他顯示卡。<br />\n<br />\n關於訂購隊伍處理<br />\n本公司已於 4 月 10 日逐一聯絡剩餘約十位客戶安排退訂或按照客戶意願作分貨安排。<br />\n飛馬電腦網站現時已不接受任何顯示卡預訂，並於網站實時顯示庫存，以便各買家作參考。<br />\n而預訂方案則會改為以填寫Google Form的形式，記錄顧客預訂之產品型號及聯絡方法，且不收取任何訂金。<br />\n同時本公司亦會開放投訴渠道予其他不滿客戶，因應不同個案去作出相應處理。<br />\n如有任何遺漏或投訴，請以 Whatsapp 聯絡 95408014 ，或電郵 complaint@pegasus.hk，我們保證盡快處理及盡力滿足各位的需求。<br />\n<br />\n除以上投訴外，我們亦收到其他不同用戶的意見及投訴，當中或有遺漏，歡迎各位於下方留言，我們會於 15 日下午 3 時前收集問題，並於下午 3 時 - 7 時進行你問我答，解答大家的問題。<br />\n<br />\n最後，再一次為因本公司突然更改條款而受影響的各位客戶致最高的歉意，令客人於購買過程當中有不如意的體驗實不為我們的本意，亦已因此從新審視內部的處理方式並作出改進。<br />\n<br />\n如對訂購產品的程序上有任何疑問或建議，歡迎各位向我們提出，本公司定當本著以客為本的精神為大家提供最好的服務，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n老細頭先已經搵左我<br />\n但係我唔會接受呢個賠償<br />\n係賠償就做好啲 <br />\n一千蚊真係寧願唔要<br />\n<br />\n另外我自己就唔會去消委海關去告佢<br />\n因為我已經退左訂 加上又麻煩同埋唔想搞到咁大<br />\n但係如果有其他苦主想爭取自己嘅權益嘅話<br />\n我都覺得係完全冇問題既<br />\n<br />\n另外嗰啲一蚊拍賣真係算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你讓比其他苦主仲好<br />\n最後個道歉真係好撚遲<br />\n之後等佢覆左再回應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbJj72et5Wf9gZDw7j2q4s6UrPDScuDdnZzwYtdpawFsV?filename=gfLw2nt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfLw2nt.png&h=5de8b6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPkqvXHjczbFxG9FYqvq7hJUvpQxKdbvkcyvn5FykSK4k?filename=ssa1E89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fssa1E89.png&h=94f868d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924a3528a2ae8c3281137212a64fc12086c7e3d8","tid":2489124,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"799b3e3abf2b02541cc02c864836753bf5a5c2d5","tid":2489124,"uid":36128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0789fb6de69e5d768d23806128c2cfe7d6f141f7","tid":2489124,"uid":177732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8ff6c880692aa860d218e6f88d1f83ef68e15098","tid":2489124,"uid":150084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"咁都要負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924b5a560526bfda6c34a0347b39d68fe17c53d2","tid":2489124,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587cd1b03106d4fd7507e8f1977f4629306a8d1e","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"等咗咁耐<br />\n搞到咁大<br />\n<br />\n賠一千蚊<br />\n真係最低工資都唔夠俾啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起價起成皮<br />\n賠就賠一千 <br />\n盤生意條數真好計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a881b6e9e1c53f426a171e93e3575c36e422537","tid":2489124,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"2911a95cea9aa42f9ea0a6e52c3949bd5ee22d3d","tid":2489124,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"3070absolutee"},{"pid":"ba8965e7121517e1344ed1fe013de78f09184ccd","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"賣咗你張卡都唔止賺一千 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcf2f758526d83220d78e079934cb8d01fa2ba2","tid":2489124,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8965e7121517e1344ed1fe013de78f09184ccd","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"賣咗你張卡都唔止賺一千 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:55:56.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2305934fa8171ffb3c5b2b3effc0e828bc04d1e","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"中立嘅林仔對個賠償有咩意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拖咗幾個月咁過份<br />\n賠一千係咪算皇恩浩蕩"},{"pid":"52ee75d095a5de93883098be07e7c4e825e2946a","tid":2489124,"uid":6530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"礦卡賺咁多捐得一千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c222df91435b30ff584ff93e140678229f08a263","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"一千蚊先啱啱夠聽 van 哥直播講兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312ec8124958afa6752696da0da97d617361f36d","tid":2489124,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c222df91435b30ff584ff93e140678229f08a263","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"一千蚊先啱啱夠聽 van 哥直播講兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e0440d181bd069be581a495141614d13b0eceb","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"一蚊抽獎<br />\n連抽七日<br />\n<br />\n送七件骨俾街坊<br />\n希望大家唔好再屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ed9c6a266c320b59d98399ec641908fcd3454f","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"312ec8124958afa6752696da0da97d617361f36d","tid":2489124,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c222df91435b30ff584ff93e140678229f08a263","tid":2489124,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"一千蚊先啱啱夠聽 van 哥直播講兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:59:51.000Z","msg":"有冇講錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}